OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FEfforts to reopen the Strait of Hormuz
OL,8,Fhave been the focus of talks between
OL,9,FUS secretary of state Marco Rubio and
OL,10,FUK Foreign Secretary Yvette Cooper.
OL,12,FThe pair discussed the ongoing Iran
OL,13,Fcrisis as Britain and France prepared
OL,14,Fto co-host a meeting of 40 defence
OL,15,Fministers on Tuesday about plans to
OL,16,Fprotect shipping in the critical
OL,17,Fwaterway once hostilities cease in the
OL,18,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FJohn Healey and his French counterpart
OL,8,FCatherine Vautrin will co-chair the
OL,9,Fsession, where the coalition partners
OL,10,Fare expected to outline the military
OL,11,Fcontributions they can make to the
OL,12,Fdefensive mission to safeguard the
OL,13,Fstrait in future.
OL,15,FThe UK has already announced the
OL,16,Fdeployment of HMS Dragon to the region
OL,17,Fso the destroyer can play a role in
OL,18,Fthe multinational mission, should the
OL,19,Fconditions allow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FSupport ship RFA Lyme Bay is also
OL,8,Fbeing converted to act as a mother
OL,9,Fship to mine-hunting drones, which
OL,10,Fcould help clear shipping lanes.
OL,12,FMr Rubio was recently critical of the
OL,13,Fpost-conflict operation, questioning
OL,14,Fthe involvement of countries "after
OL,15,Fit's over".
OL,17,FHe said: "Well, after it's over it's
OL,18,Fkind of like ` it doesn't make sense."
OL,20,FHe did then concede there may be "some
OL,21,Futility" in such an action.
OL,26,@vD@^OUwD@JO]yD@JOUzD@fO]|D@bOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FUS defence secretary Pete Hegseth has
OL,8,Fbeen more forthright, dismissing the
OL,9,Fefforts being led by the UK and France
OL,10,Fas "silly".
OL,12,FA top American military commander
OL,13,FGeneral Dan Caine has also argued "now
OL,14,Fis the time" for countries with an
OL,15,Finterest in the strait to assist the
OL,16,FUS.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@JO]uD@cOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
