PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FIn a statement issued late on Monday,
OL,8,Fstate department spokesman Tommy
OL,9,FPigott said: "Secretary of state Marco
OL,10,FRubio spoke with UK Foreign Secretary
OL,11,FYvette Cooper today to discuss Iran
OL,12,Fand ongoing efforts to restore freedom
OL,13,Fof navigation in the Strait of Hormuz."
OL,15,FThe sea route, which is a major supply
OL,16,Fline for oil and gas supplies, had
OL,17,Fbeen open prior to the US and Israel
OL,18,Flaunching strikes against Iran.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FIn retaliation, Tehran effectively
OL,8,Fclosed the shipping lane, sparking a
OL,9,Fglobal energy crisis that has seen
OL,10,Fprices rocket.
OL,12,FThis led the US to impose its own
OL,13,Fblockade of Iranian ports, leading to
OL,14,Fa stand-off.
OL,16,FAnd there looks no sign of an end to
OL,17,Fthe stalemate after Mr Trump said the
OL,18,FIran ceasefire was on "life support"
OL,19,Fand dismissed Tehran's peace proposal
OL,20,Fas "garbage", causing oil prices to
OL,21,Fagain increase sharply.
OL,26,@zD@WOUzD@dO]|D@DOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
