PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FMr Trump is expected to use a trip
OL,8,Fthis week to China to urge president
OL,9,FXi Jinping to put pressure on Iran.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the UK has issued 12 new
OL,12,Fsanctions targeting Iranians accused
OL,13,Fof planning attacks in Britain on
OL,14,Fbehalf of Tehran.
OL,16,FIn an update to the official sanctions
OL,17,Flist on Monday, the Foreign Office
OL,18,Fimposed travel bans and asset freezes
OL,19,Fon nine people for carrying out
OL,20,F"hostile activity" in the UK and
OL,21,Felsewhere.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
