OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FMs Cooper said the move "directly
OL,8,Ftargets organisations and individuals
OL,9,Fwho threaten security on UK streets
OL,10,Fand stability in the Middle East".
OL,12,FShe added: "Criminal proxies backed by
OL,13,Fparts of the Iranian regime who
OL,14,Fthreaten security int he UK and Europe
OL,15,Fwill not be tolerated, nor will
OL,16,Fillicit finance networks."
OL,26,@oD@YOUrD@aO]tD@LOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
