OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FAnother three sanctions were issued on
OL,8,Fentities including the Zindashti
OL,9,FNetwork, sanctioned last year by the
OL,10,FEU and said to be connected to Iran's
OL,11,FMinistry of Intelligence and Security.
OL,13,FAccording to the EU, the Zindashti
OL,14,FNetwork has "carried out numerous acts
OL,15,Fof transnational repression" for the
OL,16,FIranian government, including
OL,17,Fkidnappings and assassinations of
OL,18,Fcritics of the Tehran regime.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
