OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778630580
OL,3,CTransatlantic talks on Strait of
OL,4,CHormuz ahead of summit on defensive
OL,5,Cmission
OL,7,FAmong those sanctioned are five
OL,8,Fmembers of the Zarringhalam family `
OL,9,FFarhad, Fazlolah, Mansour, Nasser and
OL,10,FPouria ` said to have helped finance
OL,11,Fefforts to "destabilise" the UK.
OL,13,FMansour, Nasser and Fazlolah
OL,14,FZarringhalam were sanctioned by the US
OL,15,Flast year for their involvement in
OL,16,FIran's "shadow banking" network.
OL,26,@sD@LOUsD@XO]xD@HOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
