OL,7,FOthers accused of "threatening,
OL,8,Fplanning or conducting attacks" in the
OL,9,FUK or elsewhere include Turkish
OL,10,Fnational Ekrem Oztunc, Azerbaijani
OL,11,Fnational Namiq Salifov and Iranian
OL,12,Fnational Nihat Abdul Kadir Asan.
